<body background="images/blutxtr3.jpg" bgcolor="#A4B1B9">
<h1><font color="#0000A0"><font size=7><em><strong>ShareWorld Tech Support</strong></em></font></font></h1>
<p><a href="swindex.htm"><img src="images/bhome.gif" alt="[Home Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=56 height=14></a><a href="news.htm"><img src="images/bnews.gif" alt="[What's New Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=58 height=14></a><a href="serv01.htm"><img src="images/bservs.gif" alt="[Products Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=57 height=14></a><a href="feedback.htm"><img src="images/bfeed.gif" alt="[Feedback Icon]" align=bottom border=0 width=59 height=14></a></p>
<p><img src="images/div.gif" alt="[HRule Image]" align=bottom width=465 height=7> </p>
<h2>ShareWorld Support</h2>
<p>Support for users of ShareWorld Systems comes in a variety of forms. First, there is the excellent many 
faceted help system built into our software. here is a representative screen shot...</p>
<p><img src="images/swtech20.gif" align=bottom width=593 height=809></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>In addition to help forums, a help from other users buddy system, on line help, and email help from tech 
support and the system operator, ShareWorld systems also maintain a 10 AM to 10 PM (EST) telephone 
help system with courteous and highly skilled tech support people answering and providing assistance.</p>
<h2><img src="images/div.gif" alt="[HRule Image]" align=bottom width=465 height=7> </h2>
