<h2>Applying To ZMI</h2>

<p>ZMI runs each June. We only accept applications beginning in
the prior January and through the prior April. This is essential
for planning purposes.</p>

<p>The application is available in the relevant issues of Z
Magazine. It is rather long and complex and we appreciate if
people use the efficient form provided for the purpose in those
issues. There are matters of fees, scholarships, preferred
project groups, and so on, to account for. </p>

<p>We thank you for your interest. If you have questions that
aren't addressed somewhere in this site, please email us and we
will get back to you as promptly as we can. </p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
</body>
