experience.

<ul>
<li><b><A HREF="http://www.kei.com/irc.html">IRC FAQ</A> (Frequently Asked
Questions)
<li><a
href="http://mistral.enst.fr/~pioch/IRC/IRCprimer/IRCprimer/IRCprimer.html">
A short IRC primer</a></b>
</ul>

<P>LOL provides an IRC tool, again on the <!--HREF HERE-->Internet Page. Please
consult the instructions there and in the tool's help system for further
guidance.

<center><table border><P>Go back to the <a href="guide.htm">Left On Line
Guide to the Internet</a></table></center>

</BODY></HTML>



