        <td valign="top" width="76%">&nbsp;<img
        src="images/subban.gif" width="298" height="14"
        naturalsizeflag="0"> <p>As an individual ShareWorld
        subscriber, you get access to a members-only Web system
        which includes the following content areas: </p>
        <blockquote>
            <ul>
                <li>Diverse offerings from the sponsoring organizations,
                    such as The Nation Archives, or The
                    Wilderness Society's studies on the environment.<br>
                    </li>
                <li>Extensive guidance with Web Browsing, including
                    reviews of useful and fun progressive sites.<br>
                    </li>
                <li>Political, educational, and other topical
                    Forums often led by noted activists and
                    scholars, and without harassment and flaming.<br>
                    </li>
                <li>Online education from well renowned faculty.<br>
                    </li>
                <li>Members will be able to voice their views through
                    online polls and agenda setting forums from
                    affiliated organizations.<br>
                    </li>
                <li>Book and Magazine Clubs for sharing experiences
                    and reviews, discussing works, interacting
                    with authors and publishers, and getting
                    discounts on selected titles.<br>
                    </li>
                <li>Private teleconferencing with live chat and
                    audio capability.<br>
                    </li>
                <li>Online interactive games like chess,
                    checkers, etc.</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
                <li>A Children's Center and Children's Internet help,
                    homework and pen-pal facilities, including the
                    ability to limit web browsing access. <br>
                    </li>
                <li>Sensible adult socializing, an on line buddy system,
                    and Internet help for adults. <br>
                    </li>
                <li>Activism by fax and email on hot issues.<br>
                    </li>
                <li>Job offerings where people can post and find listings
                    of available jobs at non-profit organizations
                    and socially responsible businesses.</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
                <li>An online News Journal and online Poetry Journal
                    each written and edited by system users for
                    system users.</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
                <li>Our own online weekly international magazine, Marble,
                    with noted writers from all over the world.</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
                <li>Regular News Reports, Activism Update, Web Reviews,
                    Games, Shopping, and much more as the
                    community grows.</li>
            </ul>
        </blockquote>
        <p>All of the above takes place in a civil, supportive
        environment of like-minded members.</p>
        <p>&nbsp;<font size="1"> </font></p>
        <h3>What ShareWorld Costs </h3>
        <p><i>ShareWorld Member Fees </i></p>
        <p>ShareWorld's monthly subscription fee is $8. When you
        join any of the ShareWorld members-only systems, you get
        a user ID and password and then have unlimited access to
        all members-only ShareWorld areas listed above as well as
        to the specific content areas provided by the sponsoring organization
        you are supporting. </p>
        <p>The sponsoring organization of your system will
        receive $1 of your monthly subscription to benefit their
        campaigns, allowing the organizations to spend less time
        fundraising and more time on their mission. </p>
        <p>Users can also join additional private systems beyond
        the first (which costs $8 a month) for only $2 a month,
        half of which goes to the new sponsoring organization. </p>
        <p><i>Internet Access</i> <i>Fees</i> </p>
        <p>If you require Internet access, or want to switch to a
        reliable low cost provider and help benefit your
        participating organization by doing so, please consider
        Prodigy Internet. For ShareWorld members, Prodigy offers
        unlimited access, exceptional services, and no startup or
        software fees. For a monthly rate of $19.95 per month,
        you get unlimited local-call Web access, including space
        for your own personal web page. </p>
        <p>The sponsoring organizations will receive $10 after
        you use Prodigy Internet for 3 months, and $1 per month
        of your ongoing internet fees for as long as you maintain
        your Prodigy account. To benefit your favorite organizations,
        you must make the transition from your current provider
        to Prodigy once you join a ShareWorld system. If you are
        already a ShareWorld Member, click here to sign up for <a
        href="prodigy.htm">Prodigy Internet</a>, or for more info
        about Prodigy services.</p>
        <p>&nbsp; </p>
        <h3>How You Help Participating Organizations </h3>
        <p>By joining a ShareWorld system sponsored by a
        participating non-profit organization or socially
        responsible business, you will be supporting that organization
        or business in two very important ways: </p>
        <p>(1) A portion of your monthly subscription fees and
        Internet access fees will be going directly to the
        organization in the form of monthly payments from
        ShareWorld and Prodigy. This will help the organizations
        financially support their campaigns. </p>
        <p>Also, (2) you will be in close contact with the
        organization's staff and other members on a regular
        basis. This will allow you to influence the organization's
        policies and campaigns, and to participate in grassroots lobbying
        and other activist efforts. </p>
        <p align="center"><i>We hope you enjoy being a part of
        ShareWorld Online Communities</i> </p>
        <p align="center"><a href="sub.htm"><img
        src="images/top.gif" border="0" width="192" height="14"></a> </p>
        <p><br>
        </p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p align="center">&nbsp; </p>
</body>
