<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#72203A" link="#0001FF">
<p><img src="images/swlogo.gif" align=bottom width=546 height=134 naturalsizeflag="0"></p>
<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=600>
<tr><td align=center valign=top width=22%><a href="swhome.htm"><img src="images/welon.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=84 height=56 naturalsizeflag="0"></a><br>
<a href="sub.htm"><img src="images/subserv.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=84 height=56 naturalsizeflag="0"></a><br>
<a href="org.htm"><img src="images/orgserv.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=84 height=56 naturalsizeflag="0"></a><br>
&#160;<a href="part.htm"><img src="images/part.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=84 height=56 naturalsizeflag="0"></a><br>
<a href="faq.htm"><img src="images/faq.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=84 height=56 naturalsizeflag="0"></a><br>
<a href="memb.htm"><img src="images/members.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=84 height=56 naturalsizeflag="0"></a><br>
<a href="staff.htm"><img src="images/staff.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=84 height=56 naturalsizeflag="0"></a><br>
<a href="join.htm"><img src="images/join.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=84 height=56></a></td><td align=center valign=top width=2%><img src="images/line.gif" align=texttop width=10 height=720 naturalsizeflag="2" valign="TOP"><br>
</td><td valign=top width=76%>&#160;<img src="images/welcome.gif" align=bottom width=374 height=15 naturalsizeflag="0"> <p>ShareWorld is many things to a variety people and organizations, described 
in detail on the following pages. <i>(Select the relevant buttons on the left.)</i> </p>
<p>ShareWorld... </p>
<ul>
<li>Helps non-profit organizations (e.g. The Wilderness Society) and 
socially responsible businesses (e.g. The Nation) develop an online 
presence for their constituencies with no financial expenditure or risk.<br>
</li>
<li>Creates customized public and member-only Web systems for 
progressive organizations.<br>
</li>
<li>Promotes these online services to the sponsoring organizations' 
members to bring their members and customers onto the Internet in a 
progressive online community.<br>
</li>
<li>Edits and develops content for this progressive community, linking 
individual members of the various organizations through cross 
constituency interactions in areas such as Forums, the Online School, 
activism projects, and the Socially Responsible Store. </li>
</ul>
<p>Individual users (subscribers) pay a monthly fee to ShareWorld for access 
to the sponsoring organizations' members-only Web systems and 
ShareWorld content areas. A significant portion of the fees is contributed 
directly back to the subscriber's sponsoring organization. The sponsoring 
organizations therefore benefit from substantial revenues at no financial risk. 
Subscribers appreciate that their online spending is benefiting the causes and 
organizations about which they care deeply. </p>
<p>&#160; </p>
<h3>ShareWorld Mission and Vision </h3>
<p>ShareWorld's mission is to create an online community of progressive 
subscribers and participating organizations. ShareWorld works with these 
individuals and organizations to promote communication, raise 
consciousness, develop avenues for online activism, and assist in the growth 
and development of progressive projects. </p>
<p>&#160; </p>
<h3>Community and Business Goals </h3>
<p>ShareWorld's goal is to create, within three years, an online community of 
300,000 individual subscribers linked across 25 members-only Web 
systems sponsored by participating non-profit organizations and socially 
responsible businesses. Participating organizations will benefit from easier 
and more frequent interaction with their members and significant ongoing 
revenue to help fund their campaigns. </p>
<p>&#160; </p>
<h3>What Does a ShareWorld Community Look Like? </h3>
<p>ShareWorld is a civil and supportive members-only community of 
like-minded progressive users, with content-rich areas specifically designed 
for the interests of the community. The content is only limited by the 
imagination, skills, and talents of our contributors, members, and 
participating organizations. </p>
<p>For a list of features that subscribers enjoy, please click the Subscriber 
Services icon in the menu bar at the top of this page. </p>
<p align=center>Thank you for viewing our site... please send us <a href="mailto:gcigale@sharegroup.com">feedback</a>. </p>
<p align=center><a href="swhome.htm"><img src="images/top.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=192 height=14></a> </p>
<p align=center><br>
</p>
