<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type"
content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1">
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 2.0">
<title>Join ShareWorld</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#72203A" link="#0001FF">

<p><img src="images/swlogo.gif" width="546" height="134"
