        src="images/line.gif" align="texttop" width="9"
        height="648" naturalsizeflag="2" valign="TOP"></td>
        <td valign="top" width="76%">&nbsp;<img
        src="images/joinban.gif" width="200" height="14"
        naturalsizeflag="0"> <p><i>THANK YOU FOR YOUR INTEREST IN
        SHAREWORLD. WE THINK THAT IF YOU TRY IT OUT AND
        PARTICIPATE IN THE COMMUNITY, YOU'LL WANT TO STAY A LONG
        TIME!</i></p>
        <p>Read all 4 steps on this page before clicking.</p>
        <p><b>STEP 1: </b></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Test drive a ShareWorld members-only system by
                choosing one of the organizations in our MEMBERS
                ONLY section (click to the left). You will enter
                the system but have only limited access. You will,
                however, be able to get a good feel for what is
                available. All of the systems share many
                ShareWorld content areas, but each has unique
                content areas created for and frequented only by
                members of the organization's online system. </li>
        </ul>
        <p><b>STEP 2: </b></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Decide to join because the content and community
                is worth the 8 bucks each month. Especially since
                a part of the $8 will go directly to the
                sponsoring organization to pay for their
                campaigns.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><b>STEP 3:</b> </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Select the JOIN Button in the main menu of the
                system you are visiting. You will be asked for
                your credit card information for payment, and
                will be allowed 3 free hours or 15 free days to
                check everything out before being billed. You
                will not be billed until you go beyond the
                allotted free time.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><b>STEP 4: </b></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Become an active member of a growing progressive
                online community. Participate in a friendly and
                thoughtful environment through forums, school
                courses, book clubs, and other interactive areas.</li>
        </ul>
        <p align="center"><i>We hope you enjoy being a part of
        ShareWorld Online Communities,</i></p>
        <p align="center"><i>and please consider </i><a
        href="http://www.shareworld.com/prodigy.htm"><i>Prodigy
        Internet</i></a><i> for unlimited Internet access.</i><br>
        </p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

