    <blockquote>
        <h2><font color="#961814"><em>What Is <!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="client on line" startspan
        -->Left On Line<!--webbot bot="Substitution" endspan
        i-checksum="17324" -->?</em></font></h2>
        <p>Welcome to a descriptive account of <!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="client on line" startspan
        -->Left On Line<!--webbot bot="Substitution" endspan
        i-checksum="17324" --> (or <!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" -->), a
        continuous town meeting and intellectual and activist
        service center for large sectors of the progressive
        community. <!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" --> is a
        place to...</p>
        <blockquote>
            <dl>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1"> get useful
                    information </dt>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1">exchange
                    ideas </dt>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1"> develop new
                    political program and unity </dt>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1"> engage in on
                    line activism </dt>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1"> acclimate to
                    new technologies </dt>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1"> meet new
                    people </dt>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1"> enjoy and
                    educate oneself </dt>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1"> browse the
                    WWW with guidance </dt>
            </dl>
        </blockquote>
        <p><!--webbot bot="Substitution" s-variable="col"
        startspan -->LOL<!--webbot bot="Substitution" endspan
        i-checksum="538" --> doesn't have uncivil behavior,
        flaming, sexism, commericalism...but it does have a
        community of people seeking to understand society to
        change it for the better. </p>
    </blockquote>
</blockquote>

<p><img src="redline.gif" width="432" height="4"
naturalsizeflag="3"></p>

<blockquote>
    <blockquote>
        <h2><font color="#961814"><em>What Is ShareWorld?</em></font></h2>
        <p><a
        href="http://www.lol.shareworld.com/share/swhome.htm">ShareWorld</a>
        is an encompassing community of online systems, one of
        which is <!--webbot bot="Substitution" s-variable="col"
        startspan -->LOL<!--webbot bot="Substitution" endspan
        i-checksum="538" -->.</p>
        <p>ShareWorld creates member-only systems for diverse
        progressive organizations such as The Wilderness Society
        (WOL), The Nation Magazine (NOL), Greenpeace (GOL), and
        our system (<!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" -->).
        ShareWorld not only creates but also maintains and
        operates the technology, handles support, etc. for all
        these systems. ShareWorld also provides diverse
        additional content beyond that offered by each sponsoring
        organization and provides linkage between these systems
        for sharing of their diverse offerings internally.</p>
    </blockquote>
</blockquote>

<p><img src="redline.gif" width="432" height="4"
naturalsizeflag="3"></p>

<blockquote>
    <blockquote>
        <h2><font color="#961814"><em><!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" -->'s
        Contents</em></font></h2>
        <p><!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="client on line" startspan -->Left On Line<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="17324" --> is a
        Web Site system that offers (or has under construction)
        diverse technical, social, and informational features
        such as:</p>
        <blockquote>
            <dl>
                <dt><img src="dot.gif" align="middle" width="20"
                    height="20" naturalsizeflag="1"> an online
                    school, three semesters a year</dt>
