<body background="wback.gif" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#FF0000"
vlink="#FF0000">

<p align="left"><font color="#FF0000"><img src="wline.gif"
width="432" height="4"></font></p>

<blockquote>
    <blockquote>
        <p align="left"><font color="#FF0000"><img src="ani4.gif"
        width="281" height="103"></font></p>
    </blockquote>
</blockquote>

<p align="left"><font color="#FF0000"><img src="wguide.gif"
width="432" height="30"></font></p>

<blockquote>
    <blockquote>
        <p align="left"><font color="#000080" size="5"><em><strong>Welcome
        to the <!--webbot bot="Substitution" s-variable="col"
        startspan -->LOL<!--webbot bot="Substitution" endspan
        i-checksum="538" --> Web Guide</strong></em></font></p>
    </blockquote>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
    <blockquote>
        <p align="left"><font size="3">The Web Guide area of <!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" --> is meant
        to help you find what you need on the World Wide Web,
        with a progressive skew on the Web.</font></p>
        <p align="left">To start, it includes our <font
        color="#000000" size="3">Web Tutorials to help<strong> </strong></font>you
        feel more comfortable with the Web, and make your surfing
        more efficient.</p>
        <p align="left">The Web Guide also includes a menu with a
        set of categories each of which opens a page that lists
        relevant site reviews from <!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" --> staff and
        members, as well as search tools for that topical area.
        The menu also has an <!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" --> Home
        Pages entry that brings you to home pages created by
        other members of our system, and an <!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" --> Favorites
        entry with links to sites chosen by other members. You
        can add your own personal home page to the system, with
        information about you or your work, etc., which anyone
        anywhere on the internet can access, and you can also add
        your own favorite sites to the list of member's
        recommended offerings.</p>
        <p align="left">The areas of interest we already provide
        guides for are art, computers, ecology, feminism, gay and
        lesbian sites, health, kids, labor, magazines, movies,
        music, weather, and Zines.</p>
        <p align="left">Of course, these links within the web
        guide component of <font size="3"><!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" --> </font>are
        not the only guides to web use within the <!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" --> system.
        Rather, almost every other area within <font size="3"><!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" -->, such as
        our </font>Book Club, News section, Activism offerings,
        Research tools, and childrens section, includes not only
        links to our unique <!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" -->
        offerings, but also guides to regularly updated lists of
        what we think are the best current related Web options
        and sites.</p>
        <p align="left">In short, one of the virtues of <!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" -->
        membership is extensive up-to-date guidance in the
        efficient and informative use of the broader World Wide
        Web.</p>
        <p align="center"><a
        href="http://www.lol.shareworld.com/leftonl/visitabout.htm"><font
        size="2" face="Arial"><strong>Return to About LOL's
        Features </strong></font></a></p>
        <p align="center"><a
        href="http://www.lol.shareworld.com/leftonl/lolvis.htm"><font
        size="2" face="Arial"><strong>Return to About LOL</strong></font></a></p>
        <blockquote>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
        </blockquote>
        <p align="left">&nbsp;</p>
        <p align="left">&nbsp;</p>
    </blockquote>
</blockquote>
