        <p>Online activism can be an effective tool for seeking
        social change. It can help people understand what is
        going on, learn lessons, develop agendas and solidarity,
        and join actual campaigns via E-Mail and faxes or other
        interactive techniques.</p>
    </blockquote>
</blockquote>

<p><img src="resban.gif" width="432" height="30"
naturalsizeflag="3"></p>

<blockquote>
    <blockquote>
        <p align="left">Regarding the Web and the Internet more
        broadly, we offer three kinds of assistance to our users.</p>
        <blockquote>
            <p align="left"><font size="2" face="Arial"><strong><img
            src="http://199.172.47.21/LeftOnL/IMAGES/tandot.gif"
            align="middle" width="20" height="20"></strong></font>
            Regularly updated Guides to diverse resources on the
            WWW.</p>
