            src="http://199.172.47.21/LeftOnL/IMAGES/tandot.gif"
            align="middle" width="20" height="20"></strong></font>
            Courses in how to best use the Internet from an
            activist perspective.</p>
            <p align="left"><font size="2" face="Arial"><strong><img
            src="http://199.172.47.21/LeftOnL/IMAGES/tandot.gif"
            align="middle" width="20" height="20"></strong></font>
            Forums to exchange experiences and advice on Internet
            activism.</p>
        </blockquote>
        <p align="left">But beyond helping with activism via the
        broader Internet, <!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" --> offers a
        variety of immediate activism opportunities in our own
        system. </p>
        <blockquote>
            <p align="left"><font size="2" face="Arial"><strong><img
            src="http://199.172.47.21/LeftOnL/IMAGES/tandot.gif"
            align="middle" width="20" height="20"></strong></font>
            An Activism Update provides regularly updated reports
            on activism throughout the country.</p>
            <p align="left"><font size="2" face="Arial"><strong><img
            src="http://199.172.47.21/LeftOnL/IMAGES/tandot.gif"
            align="middle" width="20" height="20"></strong></font>
            Activism Bulletins provide news of up to the minute
            emergency campaigns</p>
            <p align="left"><font size="2" face="Arial"><strong><img
            src="http://199.172.47.21/LeftOnL/IMAGES/tandot.gif"
            align="middle" width="20" height="20"></strong></font>
            Each ShareWorld System sponsors a variety of activist
            campaigns. You can participate in these via links in
            our Activism Table of Contents Menus. </p>
            <p align="left"><font size="2" face="Arial"><strong><img
            src="http://199.172.47.21/LeftOnL/IMAGES/tandot.gif"
            align="middle" width="20" height="20"></strong></font>
            Forums about activism and activism-related issues
            facilitate user agenda setting, learning, organizing,
            etc.</p>
            <p align="left"><font size="2" face="Arial"><strong><img
