        s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" -->U is an
        online university with courses sponsored not only by <!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" s-variable="col" startspan -->LOL<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="538" -->, but also
        by other ShareWorld Online Communities organizations and
        ShareWorld itself. Various options explain how the school
        works in more detail, and allow you to enroll for a
        course online. Members take courses using our Forum
        facilities. The school is held three semesters a year.
        The first semester will have about 10 courses beginning
        March 1, and the school will grow from there. </td>
