<p align="left"><img src="IMAGES/brnwelba.gif"></p>

<blockquote>
    <blockquote>
        <p><font size="3">The <!--webbot bot="Substitution"
        s-variable="client on line" startspan -->Left On Line<!--webbot
        bot="Substitution" endspan i-checksum="17324" --></font>
        Book Club<font size="3"> is more than just a place to buy
        books. It </font>provides a number of services for
        buyers, readers, and researchers of books.</p>
        <p><font size="3">A variety of progressive publishers
        have become participants of the Book Club with more added
        weekly. Using the book club you can...</font></p>
        <p><font size="3"><img src="IMAGES/brndot.gif" width="20"
        height="20"> Purchase books online conveniently and at a
        discount.</font></p>
        <p><font size="3"><img src="IMAGES/brndot.gif" width="20"
