<HR SIZE=4></center><img align=left height=140 width=150 src="books.gif">
<H4>Commitment to client service remains as important a component of our philosophy today
as it did when we welcomed our first clients more than a century ago.  Our goal is to provide to
our clients, efficiently and economically, the quality legal service and work product that have
placed our firm in the forefront of the legal community.  In the course of responding to client
needs, our range of services has expanded, enabling us to address the complex legal issues faced
by our clients. Our firm's principal office is in <A HREF="contact.htm#dallas"><B>Dallas, Texas,</B></A> with additional offices in <A HREF="contact.htm#austin"><B>Austin, Texas,</B></A> and
<A HREF="contact.htm#NO"><B>New Orleans, Louisiana.</B></A> <p>
