<title>Locke Purnell Rain Harrell - Mission</title>
</header>
<center>
<img SRC="lprh_grn.gif"> 
<body background="linen.gif" text="000000" link="2F4F2F" vlink="A62A2A">
</center>
<p>
<pr>
<br>
<hr>

<h2><center>Our Philosophy </h2></center><blockquote>
Commitment to client service remains as important a component of our philosophy today as it did
when we welcomed our first clients more than a century ago.  Our goal is to provide to our clients,
efficiently and economically, the quality legal service and work product that have placed our firm
in the forefront of the legal community.  In the course of responding to client needs, our range of
services has expanded, enabling us to address the complex legal issues faced by our clients.
<p>



