<BR>Scott &amp; Coon Neurosurgery Associates
<BR>Southwest Medical Center Pathology Associates
<BR>Southwest Urology Associates
<BR>St. Francis Medical Center
<BR>State of Louisiana Department of Health and Hospitals
<BR>Texas Cardiology Consultants, P.A.
<BR>Thibodaux Hospital and Health Centers
<BR>Tulane Medical Center
