<TITLE>m-labor.htm </TITLE>
<BODY background="linen.gif" text="000000" link="2F4F2F" vlink="A62A2A">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="lprh_grn.gif">


<P><!--Phyllis Guin requested that I transfer a copy of this document to her --><!--2/3/95 so that
she can update it adding in the N.O. group.  She would also --><!--like to create a document that
