<TITLE>m-oil.htm </TITLE>
<BODY background="linen.gif" text="000000" link="2F4F2F" vlink="A62A2A">
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="lprh_grn.gif">

<P><!--Revised 10/18/95 per Dale Gillette-->

<P><B>LOCKE PURNELL RAIN HARRELL</B>
<BR><B>(A Professional Corporation)</B>
<P><B><U>OIL AND GAS MATTERS</B></U>
</CENTER>
<P> Our oil and gas practice group has represented private investors, independent producers,
individual landowners, publicly owned and independent oil and gas companies, and major
multinational oil and gas companies.  We advise clients with regard to oil and gas financing,
leasing, the sale and acquisition of oil and gas properties and companies, structuring of
exploration and production transactions, marketing agreements between producers and pipeline
concerns, joint venture agreements, operating agreements, state and federal regulatory issues, the
marketing and trading of oil, gas and petroleum products, and matters involving foreign
production concessions and domestic retailing operations.
<P><LI TYPE=DISK> We regularly advise clients in connection with disputes arising in oil and
gas operations including matters involving:
<BR><LI> Gas gathering, processing, distribution
<BR><LI> Gas contracts
<BR><LI> Joint operations and joint operating agreements
<BR><LI> Title disputes
<BR><LI> Surface damage disputes
<BR><LI> Regulatory compliance proceedings
<BR><LI> Products processing disputes
<BR><LI> Joint venture disputes
<BR><LI> Contract disputes on sale or purchase of properties
<BR><LI> Accounting for operations
<BR><LI> Oil and gas lease provisions


