<!-- WP Comment LAST UPDATE 5/96 -->
<center><b>BARBARA McCOMAS ANDERSON</center></b><p>
<p>
<b> SHAREHOLDER<p>
Estate Planning, Probate, Trusts and Estate Administration<p>
Tax<p>
</b><p>
<b> <i>Practice Areas</b></i><p>
<p>
<i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Substantial experience in:</i><p>
<p>
<b> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;estate administration of simple to very large or complex estates  <p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;drafting simple to complex wills <p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;drafting trusts, ranging from minor's education trusts to charitable
trusts to generation-skipping dynasty trusts  <p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;marital property planning, including pre- and post-marital agreements  <p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the division of property upon divorce, both tax and community
property aspects  <p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;contested and non-contested probate and guardianship proceedings  <p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;family partnerships created for asset management and/or tax reduction <p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;asset preservation planning <p>
</b><p>
