<center><b> PHYLLIS GUIN CANCIENNE</center></b><p>
<p>
<b> SENIOR ASSOCIATE<p>
Litigation/Labor/Employment</b><p>
<p>
<p>
<i><b> Practice Areas</b><p>
</i><p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<i><b> Substantial experience in:</b></i><p>
<p>
<b> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Representation of employers in all aspects of employment law before state
and federal courts, the Equal Employment Opportunity Commission, the
Louisiana Civil Service Commission, and the Louisiana Human Rights
Commission; <p>
<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Review and drafting of employment handbooks and policies; and <p>
<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;General commercial litigation, with particular experience in the areas of
antitrust, unfair competition, and complex contract litigation. <p>
</b><p>
<p>
<i><b> Education</b></i><p>
<p>
