&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b> *</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;New Orleans Bar Association (Vice-Chair, Continuing Legal Education
Committee; Committee Member, &quot;It's the Law&quot; Television Program) <p>
<p>
<p>
