</i><p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b> *</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Frequent author and speaker for human resource associations, employer
groups, and bar associations in the areas of labor and employment law. <p>
