leveraged equipment leasing transactions<p>
<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<!-- WP Style Open:  -->*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<!-- WP Style End:  -->
Representation of business entities in transactions with state and local government
entities, including public-private transactions, licensing proceedings, and public finance
transactions<p>
<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<!-- WP Style Open:  -->*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<!-- WP Style End:  -->
Representation of government entities in contract negotiations and other transactions
with private sector business entities<p>
