consisting of a follow-on offering by NCI&nbsp;Building Systems, Inc., an initial public offering by
Gadzooks, Inc. and a follow-on offering by Papa John's International, Inc. <p>
<p>
Charles&nbsp;E. Smith Residential Realty, Inc. - Represented issuer in a public roll-up of general
and limited partnerships and an initial public offering of NYSE-listed real estate investment
trust.<p>
<p>
Bear, Stearns &amp; Co., Inc. - Represented Bear, Stearns in a follow-on public offering by
Summit Technology, Inc.<p>
<p>
Various Parties - Represented various parties in a variety of corporate governance and
organization, regulatory compliance, financing, acquisition and securities law matters as well
as various partnership law matters.<p>
